mods.abstract: Page 2 of the album includes three photographs.; Photograph 1 [250] shows young plants in an outdoor seed bed with a brick wall in the background.; Photograph 2 [251] shows rows of young crops with a building and trees in the background.; Photograph 3 [252] shows rows of crops with trees in the background.
mods.note: Photograph 1 was published in the following journal. Kelley, E.B, Powell, O. & Tiebout, G.L. (1914, July) The Vegetable Garden. University Bulletin, Vol. 5, N.S. (No. 7), p.18. Photograph is captioned, "Young Seed Plants in Outdoor Seed Bed."
